==制作==
该片改编自[[澳大利亚文学|澳大利亚女性小说家]]{{Link-en|多莉丝·皮尔金顿·加利梅拉|Doris Pilkington Garimara}}的长篇小说《{{Link-en|防兔篱笆|Follow the Rabbit-Proof Fence}}》，反映了1905年起[[澳大利亚政治|澳大利亚当局]]对土著人的暴政，当局对他们实行“[[混血儿|混血改造人种计划]]”、“[[西化|西化]]”、“英语化”、“习俗英国化”等，使得他们成了“[[被偷走的一代|被偷走的一代]]”，电影通过三个小女孩的命运控诉了澳大利亚当局和[[英帝国|英帝国]][[殖民|殖民者]]。<ref name="Pilkington">{{cite journal |last= Brewster |first= Anne |authorlink= |coauthors= |title= The Stolen Generations: Rites of Passage: Doris Pilkington interviewed by Anne Brewster (22 January 2005) |journal= The Journal of Commonwealth Literature |volume = 42 |issue = 1 |pages = 143–159 |year= 2007 |url= |doi= 10.1177/0021989407075735 |id= |accessdate=25 July 2007 }}</ref>

该片在澳大利亚的票房是US$3,756,418，在美国的票房是$6,199,600，在全球的票房是$16,217,411。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=rabbitprooffence.htm |title=Rabbit-Proof Fence (2002) - International Box Office Results |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2 December 2007 |accessdate=16 May 2010 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131074134/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=rabbitprooffence.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=rabbitprooffence.htm |title=Rabbit-Proof Fence (2002) |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2 December 2007 |accessdate=16 May 2010 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131074531/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=rabbitprooffence.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

